title: Sukh Sagar Kandivali Mumbai
typeOfFood: Lacto, Chinese, Indian, Juice bar, Catering
description: Restaurant chain originated in India and branched out to many locations. The extensive menu includes cuisines from North Indian tandoor and Punjabi as well as snacks, pizza, Chinese dishes, desserts, fresh juices, and beverages. Established in 2006 and seats 150.
